{
  "stem": "353.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because my father made a-- from [? other ?] room in our house, made a shul, because the shuls were closed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then, when I came back, all shuls are closed, and people were playing in our house in one of our rooms.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Further on, my-- my youngest brother was bar mitzvahed in 1940.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, I was staying outside on the street to watch him go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Gestapo, Germans or SS or somebody's not coming.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Closer to our house.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Shouldn't be heard that somebody's praying and lives in this apartment.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's what the-- the way how we were afraid of the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The war started September 2nd.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Nazis came to Krakow, I think-- because I was not at home then.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before the invasion, when we knew that they are already in [? villages ?] like Katowice.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we started to move out from home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, then, during this time, we-- I experienced when I came back, we experienced the a Pole who become a volksdeutscher, became a German.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He came up to my father and said, 'Now, I'm going to move to your apartment.' And we got, I think, a day or two time to move out.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, I moved-- we moved out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where did you move to?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father moved to outside the city, not in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were in Niepolomice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I will tell you right away why this came out together.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the same time, we supposed to get Kennkarte, who is allowed to stay in the city of Krakow, and who has to leave the city of Krawkow.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I and my younger brother, we got to Kennkartes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the rest of my family didn't [INAUDIBLE], since they had to move anyhow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father took a apartment somewhere in a little village.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
